{"tid":1375544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真討論] 天橋嘅重要性","createTime":"2019-07-28T05:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T06:32:24.000Z","uid":1545,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"50710a406947b2a53db15dd04c648e46d4b540f8","tid":1375544,"uid":1545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"大家睇過片都記得721班狗係天橋上面當正自己狙擊手咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時會係天橋聚集嘅大部分都係花生友、傳媒、阻人影相嘅手足，班狗要上嚟佔天橋開狙擊mode根本無能力阻到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拎制空點呢樣野絕對係好重要，係要有手足係上面負責擾亂班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但假設當班狗推線推到差唔多到天橋位嘅時候，應該點樣守好條天橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔希望見到直到棄守然後重演721條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def5bcca02a58fb44a15b26370de54c1d4b35441","tid":1375544,"uid":1545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:44:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a7792cbd6cedc912c24db70818bbac7d0f69136a","tid":1375544,"uid":1545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:44:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"39116dd7d68b8dd4a173c71d9368a4171717804e","tid":1375544,"uid":1545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:44:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"77071d7e48d76a075a5f6d9da009ad95ff74149f","tid":1375544,"uid":1545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:45:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f268ef2d75d2078685eeaded75e4dd162bd664ec","tid":1375544,"uid":1545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"推到有人討論"},{"pid":"a34ee7e6af2114b7dd07f790d7bab4a4b653b53f","tid":1375544,"uid":1545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:47:48.000Z","msg":"推到有人討論"},{"pid":"ad0932786d3e0efeae60d6ba58122176fe7cec46","tid":1375544,"uid":1545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl